# supported

**Type Property**

The action should only be run when the new viewpoint is equivalent to one of the values provided through [doc://com.apple.SwiftUI/documentation/SwiftUI/View/supportedVolumeViewpoints(_:)].

## Declaration

```swift
static let supported: VolumeViewpointUpdateStrategy
```

## Discussion

The viewpoint will be equivalent to where the window bar and ornaments are presented for a volume.
